              <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
                3. Even Increases &amp; Decreases
              </h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Distribute increases or decreases evenly across a row, with a
                written instruction you can copy into your pattern.
              </p>

              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1" for="id-type"
                    >Operation</label
                  >
                  <select
                    id="id-type"
                    class="w-full border rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm"
                  >
                    <option value="increase">Increase</option>
                    <option value="decrease">Decrease</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1" for="id-start"
                    >Starting stitch count</label
                  >
                  <input
                    id="id-start"
                    type="number"
                    min="1"
                    step="1"
                    class="w-full border rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm"
                    placeholder="e.g. 80"
                  />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1" for="id-end"
                    >Final stitch count</label
                  >
                  <input
                    id="id-end"
                    type="number"
                    min="1"
                    step="1"
                    class="w-full border rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm"
                    placeholder="e.g. 96"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>

              <button
                id="btn-incdec"
                type="button"
                class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded hover:bg-blue-700"
