              </h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Use a swatch to estimate how much yarn your project will use and
                how many skeins you should buy.
              </p>

              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1" for="yarn-unit"
                    >Measurement unit</label
                  >
                  <select
                    id="yarn-unit"
                    class="w-full border rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm"
                  >
                    <option value="cm">centimeters</option>
                    <option value="in">inches</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label
                    class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1"
                    for="yarn-len-unit"
                    >Yarn length unit</label
                  >
                  <select
                    id="yarn-len-unit"
                    class="w-full border rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm"
                  >
                    <option value="m">meters</option>
                    <option value="yd">yards</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>

              <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Swatch</h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <label
                    class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1"
                    for="swatch-width"
                    >Swatch width</label
                  >
                  <input
                    id="swatch-width"
                    type="number"
                    min="0"
                    step="0.1"
                    class="w-full border rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm"
                    placeholder="e.g. 10"
                  />
